snippet.textDisplay: What a composition!! What melodies but above all, what singing... This medley of two of Shuja's masterpieces is flawlessly amalgamated and brilliantly executed full CS style by Shuja! I have listened to it some 100 times since its release and every time I am left equally mesmerized by the magic they created in studio with such versatility in pitch and voice control. They both are exceptionally talented! Lots and lots of love from an Indian from Dubai! Love Pakistani music since my college days starting with Junoon and Ali Haider and that love has continued when I heard Nusrat sahab and later Arif Lohar, Zeb & Hanya, Javed Basheer, Atif, Noori, QB, Akhtar Chanal, Sanam Marvi, Komal Rizvi,Sara Haider, Ali Zafar, Uzair and Umair Jaswal and so many more... Please continue to enthrall us with your music, we love you and someday "we shall overcome"!
